text: Edward Corrie and Daniel Smethurst were the defending champions, however Smethurst chose not to participate. Corrie partnered Frederik Nielsen but lost in the first round. Ross William Guignon and Tim Kopinski won the title, defeating Frank Dancevic and Adil Shamasdin in the final, 7–6(7–2), 6–2. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== * Main Draw JSM Challenger of Champaign-Urbana Category:JSM Challenger of Champaign–Urbana
